      "speakers": [
        "四红龙套"
      ],
      "text": "噢！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00012",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "代战公主"
      ],
      "text": "将人马扎在银空山，",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00013",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "代战公主、四红龙套、马达、江海同扯四门。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00014",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "代战公主"
      ],
      "text": "个个儿郎好威严！只因大王南朝转，倒叫咱家挂心间。耳边又听——",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00015",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "代战公主"
      ],
      "text": "雁声喊，空中大雁上下翻。开弓放出刁翎箭，",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00016",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "代战公主射雁。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00017",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "马达",
        "江海"
      ],
      "text": "大雁带箭而逃。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00018",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "代战公主"
      ],
      "text": "紧紧追赶。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00019",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四红龙套"
      ],
      "text": "噢！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00020",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四红龙套、马达、江海、代战公主同下。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00021",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "高嗣继上，起霸。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00022",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "高嗣继"
      ],
      "text": "头戴银盔明灿亮，身穿铠甲似秋霜。胯下一骑白龙马，上阵手持素银枪。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00023",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四白龙套暗同上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00024",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高嗣继"
      ],
      "text": "俺，高嗣继。奉了王丞相将令，追赶平贵。可恨代战公主，战又不战，降又不降，岂肯容她猖狂？众将官。",
      "text_length": 47
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00025",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四白龙套同允。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00026",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "高嗣继"
      ],
      "text": "迎敌者！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00027",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四白龙套同允。高嗣继上马，高嗣继、四白龙套同下。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00028",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "薛平贵上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00029",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "心中只把魏虎怨，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00030",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "俺，薛平贵。唐王晏驾，王允篡位。俺不免将金铃鸽儿放回，候公主大兵到此。魏虎哇，贼！我不杀你誓不为人也！",
      "text_length": 51
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00031",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "苦苦害我为哪般？金铃鸽儿撒回转，",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00032",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "薛平贵放鸽儿。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00033",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "等候公主报仇冤。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00034",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "薛平贵下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00035",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四红龙套引代战公主同上。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00036",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "代战公主"
      ],
      "text": "大王一去无音讯，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00037",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "马达、江海同上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00038",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "马达",
        "江海"
      ],
      "text": "鸽子回来啦！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00039",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "代战公主"
      ],
      "text": "想是大王有难。马达、江海！",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00040",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "马达",
        "江海"
      ],
      "text": "在。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00041",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "代战公主"
      ],
      "text": "吩咐兵发三关哪！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00042",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "马达",
        "江海"
      ],
      "text": "兵发三关哪！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00043",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "代战公主上马，四红龙套同走圆场。四白龙套引高嗣继同上，会阵。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00044",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "代战公主"
      ],
      "text": "问声小将名和姓？通上名来好交兵！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00045",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "高嗣继"
      ],
      "text": "老爷名叫高嗣继，我保王允坐华夷！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00046",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "代战公主"
      ],
      "text": "听说来了高嗣继，咱家与你见高低！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00047",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四红龙套、四白龙套、马达、江海同钻烟筒，自两边分下。高嗣继、代战公主同起打，自两边分下。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00048",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "薛平贵上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00049",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "金铃鸽儿撒放转，不见公主为哪般？将身来在汾河岸，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00050",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "薛平贵到小边。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00051",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "那旁又来一将官。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00052",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "高嗣继上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00053",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "高嗣继"
      ],
      "text": "催马来在汾河岸，只见平贵在面前。手持金枪分心刺，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00054",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "孤王上前忙遮拦。问声小将名和姓，刺杀孤王为哪般？",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00055",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "高嗣继"
      ],
      "text": "白马银枪高嗣继，我保王允坐江山！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00056",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "自从盘古立地天，哪有为臣坐江山？哗啦啦催开红鬃战，",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00057",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "薛平贵、高嗣继同起打，薛平贵跌下马。龙形上，舞，下。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00058",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "高嗣继"
      ],
      "text": "只见青龙头上翻。翻身下了马走战，",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00059",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "高嗣继下马，跪。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00060",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "高嗣继"
      ],
      "text": "三呼万岁饶恕咱。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00061",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "人困马乏难交战，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00062",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "薛平贵上马。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00063",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "只见小将跪马前。马上擒王擒不住，诓孤下马难上难！",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00064",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "高嗣继"
      ],
      "text": "万岁不必仔细盘，为臣保你坐江山。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00065",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "既愿保孤坐江山，你对苍天表一番！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00066",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "高嗣继"
      ],
      "text": "我若保主有假意，死在千军万马前！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00067",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "一见小将盟誓愿，不由孤王喜心间。左思右想——",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00068",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "不下马，",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00069",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "薛平贵想。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00070",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "有了！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00071",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "鞭梢搀起将魁元。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00072",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "高嗣继起。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00073",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "高嗣继"
      ],
      "text": "西凉有个女代战，她不归降也枉然。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00074",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "西凉有个女代战，她保孤王坐江山。耳旁又听人声喊，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00075",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四红龙套、代战公主同上。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00076",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "代战公主"
      ],
      "text": "来了代战女婵娟。手使金枪分心点，",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00077",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "孤王上前忙遮拦。白马银枪高嗣继，他保孤王坐江山。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00078",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "代战公主"
      ],
      "text": "既然保你坐江山，何不带兵反长安？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00079",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "好哇！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00080",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "孤王马上将令传！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00081",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "马达、江海听我言：上殿先拿王丞相，休要放走魏左参！大喊一声催前趱，",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00082",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四红龙套、高嗣继、代战公主同下。薛平贵到大边。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00083",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "薛平贵"
      ],
      "text": "薛平贵今日报仇冤。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00084",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s05",
      "scene_no": 5,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "薛平贵下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00085",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "乌鸦不住当头叫，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00086",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "魏虎持大刀引王允同上。魏虎舞刀。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00087",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "贤婿，这做什么？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00088",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "魏虎"
      ],
      "text": "在此保驾呀！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00089",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "哪有这样的保法？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00090",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "魏虎"
      ],
      "text": "这叫武保。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00091",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "还是文保的好！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00092",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "魏虎"
      ],
      "text": "还是武保的好！哇呀呀……",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00093",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "唉！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00094",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "叫得老夫心内焦。怕的是代战女兴兵到，孤王我江山坐不牢。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00095",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 95,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "魏虎"
      ],
      "text": "老丈人哪！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00096",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 96,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "魏虎"
      ],
      "text": "岳父休要心烦恼，小婿言来听根苗：哪怕那代战女兴兵到，有魏虎我会耍大刀！",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00097",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 97,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "王允"
      ],
      "text": "贤婿休要胡乱道，你保孤王坐九朝。快快摆驾金殿道，",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03021012_e00098",
      "play_id": "03021012",
      "scene_id": "03021012_s06",
      "scene_no": 6,
      "seq_global": 98,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四红龙套引马达、江海同上，擒王允、魏虎同下。（四红龙套、马达、江海、代战公主自上场门同上，四白龙套、高嗣继自下场门同上，过场，四红龙套、马达、江海、四白龙套同下。代战公主、高嗣继双耍小下场，双收，分下。）",
      "text_length": 102
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}